    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and truly looks like it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, glass-like finish, and there are no chips, scratches, or imperfections to be found anywhere on the body. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still smelling new and every electronic feature functioning perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example that has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by specialists.",
