      "description": "We are proud to offer this meticulously preserved vehicle, presenting in a state that rivals its original delivery condition. Every aspect of this automobile, from its unblemished coachwork to its pristine cabin, reflects a standard of care synonymous with collector-grade quality. Rigorously inspected and maintained with an uncompromising attention to detail, this specimen represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast seeking an investment-grade asset. We invite you to experience an automotive benchmark that defines excellence in its class.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
